{"tid":1109551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界真係痴撚線，咁多人合理化出軌","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T10:51:41.000Z","uid":230008,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c59f54854c968fdb000bdd797272c4494a93c8ab","tid":1109551,"uid":230008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"平胸又好 耶撚又好<br />\n呢個唔係出軌既理由囉好唔撚好<br />\n痴撚線點解可以有連登仔合理化呢件事<br />\n你抽一兩下水都算啦<br />\n又真係有人覺得呢個係一個合理原因架喎<br />\n個問題係<br />\n佢唔係第一日係耶撚 亦都唔係第一日冇波<br />\n晨早就知<br />\n係唔啱既就咪撚結婚<br />\n結左婚一係就管好自己碌尻一係就一早離撚左佢啦<br />\n成日都話男人用碌尻諗野唔會忍到<br />\n唔該唔好咁多籍口合理化出軌<br />\n出軌根本唔關性別事<br />\n錯就錯啦屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>願天下出軌既人死全家</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4e8aafe4db2fac7c2d80a5a228151d09fc00a534","tid":1109551,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"一夫一妻根本係人類文明退化嘅一部分"},{"pid":"900abd37f1e6005c92f99ee3cdce6ea165550b98","tid":1109551,"uid":175039,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家既意思唔係合理化出軌<br />\n純粹係仇平胸同耶撚"},{"pid":"6685dbc2ffb96e52237037c6276765edfdb85135","tid":1109551,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"900abd37f1e6005c92f99ee3cdce6ea165550b98","tid":1109551,"uid":175039,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家既意思唔係合理化出軌<br />\n純粹係仇平胸同耶撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"係，老鼠安仆街係事實<br />\n但耶撚真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋正常都唔會平到咁"},{"pid":"774c26ca45562b387387a7dcaa4ea5ede12b8c80","tid":1109551,"uid":230008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6685dbc2ffb96e52237037c6276765edfdb85135","tid":1109551,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"900abd37f1e6005c92f99ee3cdce6ea165550b98","tid":1109551,"uid":175039,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201